sequenceDiagram
    actor Host
    actor Player
    participant App as Frontend
    participant CF as Cloud Functions
    participant Auth as Firebase Auth
    participant DB as Realtime Database
    participant GMaps as Google Maps

    Note over Host,GMaps: Game Creation Flow

    Host->>App: Click "Start a game"
    App->>App: Show auth dialog
    Host->>App: Enter username
    App->>CF: login({ username })
    CF->>Auth: createCustomToken(uid)
    Auth-->>CF: token
    CF-->>App: { token, uid }
    App->>Auth: signInWithCustomToken(token)
    App->>Auth: updateProfile({ displayName })

    App->>CF: createGame(username)
    CF->>DB: Set game data (5 random rounds)
    CF->>Auth: createCustomToken(uid, { roomHost })
    CF-->>App: { roomId, token }
    App->>App: Update URL with roomId
    App->>DB: listenGameChanges(roomId)
    App->>App: Show lobby + host controls

    Note over Host,GMaps: Player Joins

    Host->>Player: Share game link
    Player->>App: Open link with ?roomId=xxx
    App->>App: Show auth dialog
    Player->>App: Enter username
    App->>CF: login({ username })
    CF-->>App: { token }
    App->>CF: joinGame(roomId, username)
    CF->>DB: Add player to game
    App->>DB: listenGameChanges(roomId)

    Note over Host,GMaps: Gameplay Loop (per round)

    Host->>App: Click "Start Game"
    App->>CF: startGame(roomId)
    CF->>DB: status=playing, roundStartedAt=now
    DB-->>App: onValue → round data
    App->>GMaps: Load Street View iframe(lat, lng)
    App->>App: Show country picker + start timer

    Player->>App: Select flag + Submit
    App->>CF: submitGuess(roomId, round, countryCode)
    CF->>CF: Calculate score (1000 + time bonus)
    CF->>DB: Update player guess + score
    DB-->>App: onValue → updated scores
    App->>App: Show result + leaderboard update

    Host->>App: Click "Next Round"
    App->>CF: nextRound(roomId)
    CF->>DB: Reveal answer, advance round

    Note over Host,GMaps: Game Over (after 5 rounds)

    CF->>DB: status=finished
    DB-->>App: onValue → finished state
    App->>App: Show final scores + winner
